OL,3,CTwo people pulled from Eryri slate
OL,4,Cmine after six-hour cave rescue
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FTwo cave explorers were pulled from an
OL,8,FEryri slate mine after six-hour cave
OL,9,Frescue operation over the weekend.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,FCroesor-Rhosydd slate mine near
OL,13,FBlaenau Ffestiniog after the pair
OL,14,Fbecame trapped underground on Sunday.
OL,16,FThree people had entered the mine, but
OL,17,Ftwo became trapped on each side of a
OL,18,Fflooded chamber. One of the trapped
OL,19,Fpair had also fallen into deep water
OL,20,Fwithin the mine.
