OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FThe third person left the mine before
OL,8,Fcalling 999, and emergency services
OL,9,Fwere called in to carry out a rescue.
OL,11,FThe North Wales Cave Rescue
OL,12,FOrganisation (NWCRO) described the
OL,13,FCroesor-Rhosydd slate mine as "a
OL,14,Fregular call-out location for the
OL,15,Fteam".
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the NWCRO, which
OL,18,Fwas called in to assist, said they
OL,19,Fwere called just before 5pm to help
OL,20,FAberglaslyn Mountain Rescue Team
OL,21,F(AMRT) with the incident.
