OL,4,Cmine after six-hour cave rescue
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FThey said: "After some initial
OL,8,Finvestigation, the team determined the
OL,9,Fincident was at the Croesor-Rhosydd
OL,10,Fslate mine which requires appropriate
OL,11,Fcaving experience, equipment and the
OL,12,Fability to both ascend and descend
OL,13,Fropes.
OL,15,F"One person exited the mine and called
OL,16,F999, reporting that two young persons
OL,17,Fwere trapped underground, one each
OL,18,Fside of a flooded chamber.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
