OL,3,CTwo people pulled from Eryri slate
OL,4,Cmine after six-hour cave rescue
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,F"One had fallen into deep water. NWCRO
OL,8,Fteam members were called out and
OL,9,Fattended from as far afield as Chester
OL,10,Fand Holyhead, some attending directly
OL,11,Ffrom the UK national caving conference
OL,12,Fat Llangollen.
OL,14,F"An advance party was dispatched to
OL,15,Ffind the two individuals left
OL,16,Funderground and establish their
OL,17,Fcondition. When found, they were given
OL,18,Fhot drinks and warm dry clothing
OL,19,Fbefore technical ropework was used to
OL,20,Fbring them to a safe location.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
