OL,3,CTwo people pulled from Eryri slate
OL,4,Cmine after six-hour cave rescue
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,F"When additional team members made
OL,8,Fcontact with the advance party, the
OL,9,Ftwo individuals were assisted out of
OL,10,Fthe mine and handed over to AMRT.
OL,12,F"While the underground rescue was
OL,13,Ftaking place, there was concern for
OL,14,Fthe person who had made the 999 call
OL,15,Fbeing alone on high ground in
OL,16,Fdeteriorating weather and falling
OL,17,Flight.
