OL,3,CTwo people pulled from Eryri slate
OL,4,Cmine after six-hour cave rescue
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,F"An AMRT party found and escorted them
OL,8,Fback to the rendezvous point where the
OL,9,Fteams were assembled. Close
OL,10,Fcooperation with AMRT was maintained
OL,11,Fthroughout what was effectively a
OL,12,Fjoint operation.
OL,14,F"Our involvement in the incident
OL,15,Flasted approximately 6.5 hours and
OL,16,Finvolved 17 NWCRO team members,
OL,17,Ftotalling in excess of 150 team hours,
OL,18,Fplus the substantial commitment from
OL,19,FAMRT who provided surface
OL,20,Fcommunications and transportation.
